{"tid":603994,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"【每日笑一笑】 鸚鵡不忿被毛巾「打」　喊到拆天似BB","createTime":"2018-03-24T09:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T09:34:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f72937e675e17a4e829d9bbb5d06b040d9a6ebc8","tid":603994,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T09:34:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180324/20341797\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180324%2F20341797&d=ZJyhSy%2F3CVi2leHjjJ8y7cn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=5510544e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180324%2F20341797&h=1764d920\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180324/20341797</a><br />\n<br />\n【每日笑一笑】<br />\n鸚鵡不忿被毛巾「打」　喊到拆天似BB<br />\n<br />\n國際新聞   <br />\n         <br />\n鸚鵡除了懂得模仿人類說話外，原來模仿小孩哭喊聲亦似模似樣。片中主人原本用毛巾作裝拍打小鸚鵡，但小鸚鵡反應非常誇張，不斷發出激似小孩扭計哭喊的聲音，越喊越淒厲，主人最終不忍抱起小鸚鵡不斷錫錫，牠才慢慢收起「哭聲」，得意地享受著主人的呵哄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMotila Rab"}]}